## EP-04 — Ratings System

> **Goal**: Allow stagiaires to rate courses and display average ratings.
> **Assigned to**: Dev B

---

### US-04.1 — Rate a Course

**As a** stagiaire,
**I want** to rate a course from 1 to 5 stars,
**So that** I can share my feedback.

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Priority | Medium |
| Story Points | 5 |
| Sprint | Sprint 2 |

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Interactive star rating (1-5)
- [ ] Optional comment field
- [ ] User can only rate once per course
- [ ] Submit button disabled until stars selected
- [ ] Rating added to list immediately

**Sub-Tasks:**
| Task | Assignee | Est. |
|------|----------|------|
| Create interactive [StarRating](file:///c:/cmclearning/src/components/ui/StarRating.tsx#11-39) component | Dev B | 1h |
| Create [CourseRatings](file:///c:/cmclearning/src/features/ratings/components/CourseRatings.tsx#14-80) component with form | Dev B | 2h |
| Implement `ratingsService.create()` | Dev B | 0.5h |
| Check if user already rated (hide form if yes) | Dev B | 0.5h |

---

