**As a** stagiaire,
**I want** to see the average rating on course cards and details,
**So that** I can identify high-quality courses.

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Priority | Medium |
| Story Points | 3 |
| Sprint | Sprint 2 |

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Star display + numeric average + total count on [CourseCard](file:///c:/cmclearning/src/features/courses/components/CourseCard.tsx#11-56)
- [ ] Same display on [CourseDetailsPage](file:///c:/cmclearning/src/features/courses/pages/CourseDetailsPage.tsx#18-146)
- [ ] Updates after new rating submitted

**Sub-Tasks:**
| Task | Assignee | Est. |
|------|----------|------|
| Add StarRating display to CourseCard | Dev B | 0.5h |
| Add average display to CourseDetailsPage | Dev B | 0.5h |
| Refresh average after new submission | Dev B | 0.5h |

---

