## EP-06 — Search & Filtering

> **Goal**: Enable users to search and filter courses across the platform.
> **Assigned to**: Dev C

---

### US-06.1 — Global Search Bar

**As a** user,
**I want** a search bar in the Navbar,
**So that** I can quickly find courses from anywhere.

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Priority | Medium |
| Story Points | 3 |
| Sprint | Sprint 2 |

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Search input in Navbar (hidden on mobile)
- [ ] Pressing Enter navigates to `/search?q=query`
- [ ] Query pre-filled on SearchPage

**Sub-Tasks:**
| Task | Assignee | Est. |
|------|----------|------|
| Add search input to Navbar | Dev C | 0.5h |
| Navigate to search page with query param on Enter | Dev C | 0.5h |
| Read query param in SearchPage and trigger search | Dev C | 0.5h |

---

