## Sprint Planning Recommendation

| Sprint | Focus | Key Stories |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| **Sprint 1** | Foundation | EP-09 (Shell), US-01.1–01.5 (Auth), US-02.1–02.2 (Course List/Detail), US-03.1 (Resource List) |
| **Sprint 2** | Core Features | US-02.3–02.6 (Course CRUD), US-03.2–03.4 (Upload/Download), US-04.1–04.2 (Ratings), US-05.1–05.4 (Forum), US-06.1–06.2 (Search), US-07.1 (Admin Stats), US-08.1–08.2 (Profile) |
| **Sprint 3** | Polish & Admin | US-05.5–05.6 (Voting), US-04.3–04.4 (Reviews), US-07.2–07.4 (Admin CRUD), US-03.5–03.6 (Resource extras), US-08.3 (Password), US-02.7 (Thumbnail) |
| **Sprint 4** | Stretch | Backlog items: password reset, search suggestions, avatar upload, charts |

---

> **Total**: 9 Epics · 35 User Stories · ~170 Story Points · 4 Sprints
